  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--but we talked to a few families, and one of them who was a well-to-do baker, actually, and the Rabbi [NON-ENGLISH], he was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said yes, it is true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Things are-- things are so far, because the Germans need us and everybody is working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was this river running, and the [NON-ENGLISH] was along the river.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's where they were washing all those-- I mean the smell was awful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were washing all those the skins, those animal skins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back with this information which we got and that's when my cousin-- then came this one episode which stuck in my mind because it was really out-- like out of a movie.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My cousin and this [NON-ENGLISH], they decided they are going to make a business out of it, so we would make-- earn some money, the two families-- and of course, this Pole also.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was all-- actually, it was all sort of not allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, if the Germans appeared-- but I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- this Pole, he hired a moving company from Warsaw, which were trucks, not horse and buggy trucks, but trucks-- water, ice trucks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started to offer it in Miedzyrzec-- who wants to go, because in Warsaw, everybody was so bad and everybody got to be so, you know, terribly concerned what to do, what to do, and where to go.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever wants to go to Miedzyrzec-- for that and that much money-- I don't know how much it was charged, and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- we would organize it, and we will-- it is-- it's a moving deal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's really what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my cousin and was this-- this [NON-ENGLISH], they were communicating with whoever was a representative of this moving company.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
